From ad88ebd5c20e4c60682cfcc12295f78dd92abb26 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: James Docherty <jamesdocherty97@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 10:44:19 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 3/6] Trim unreferenced legacy assets from repo

These eight WebP files were documented as legacy/comparison art, are not
referenced by index.html or sw.js, and lean toward the generic-football
look the visual direction avoids. They remain in the owner's local
package and handover zip.
---
 ASSET-BRIEF.md                        |  15 ++-------------
 assets/empty-album-state.webp         | Bin 111004 -> 0 bytes
 assets/football-boot-ball-detail.webp | Bin 142372 -> 0 bytes
 assets/football-goal-burst.webp       | Bin 159944 -> 0 bytes
 assets/football-matchday-action.webp  | Bin 122840 -> 0 bytes
 assets/group-table-state.webp         | Bin 151886 -> 0 bytes
 assets/handover-swap-state.webp       | Bin 99674 -> 0 bytes
 assets/milestone-complete-state.webp  | Bin 156738 -> 0 bytes
 assets/pitch-texture.webp             | Bin 63532 -> 0 bytes
 9 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 13 deletions(-)
 delete mode 100644 assets/empty-album-state.webp
 delete mode 100644 assets/football-boot-ball-detail.webp
 delete mode 100644 assets/football-goal-burst.webp
 delete mode 100644 assets/football-matchday-action.webp
 delete mode 100644 assets/group-table-state.webp
 delete mode 100644 assets/handover-swap-state.webp
 delete mode 100644 assets/milestone-complete-state.webp
